      13. Connective glossary panels
      <span class="symbolic-layer-badge" title="Observational symbolic-grammar layer — supplementary; does not change canonical classifications">observational</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      These six panels point from a glossary term to where the term lives in practice &mdash; in tricks,
      in operational notation, and in related symbolic groups. The definitions are coach-tone summaries;
      the canonical entries above remain authoritative.
    </p>
    <p class="section-intro detail-muted">
      The panels are positioned as educational bridges to the dictionary. They
      will migrate to the trick dictionary in a future slice as family/topology
